<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF207-229-504  </DOCNO><DOCID>07 229 504.andM;</DOCID><JOURNAL>MacUser  June 1989 v5 n6 p199(1)* Full Text COPYRIGHT Ziff-Davis Publishing Co. 1989.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>FRed Font Machine. (Font Resource Editor)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Parascandolo, Salvatore.andM;</AUTHOR><DESCRIPT>Company:   AB Vista Co. (product introduction).andO;Product:   FRed Font Machine (Computer program) (product introduction).andO;Topic:     FontsProduct Introduction.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>FRed Font MachineandM;The font-design field has long been dominated by Altsys' Fontographer.andP;  Butcompetition in this niche has recently heated up.andP;  FRed Font Machine (FRedstands for Font Resource Editor) is the working title for a new font-creationand font-editing package from AB Vista.andM;FRed comes with a complete set of Bezier tools for producing downloadablePostScript fonts, and it can also output font outlines and composed text inPICT and Illustrator 88 formats and EPSF.andP;  It has intelligent guidelines thathelp reduce font-construction mistakes, and it offers automatic help inmaintaining stroke weight and symmetry.andP;  Its autotrace tool can speed up theconversion of bit-mapped images into font outlines.andM;A key feature is FRed's ability to generate &quot;hints&quot; that provide high-qualityprinting on 300-dot-per-inch (dpi) PostScript laser printers.andP;  This couldenable users to add hints to other PostScript-clone fonts, such as those fromBitstream and Compugraphic.andP;  FRed Font Machine's fonts aren't encrypted, soyou can create logos and other special effects in type-manipulation programslike Broderbund's TypeStyler.andM;FRed also makes bit-mapped (screen) fonts, in black-and-white or color, andit will automatically anti-alias (dejag) grayscale fonts.andP;  Its quick-accessparts library can help maintain consistency in serifs, accents, and otherfont aspects, and your changes to a library part are reflected throughout theentire font.andP;  Multiple levels of undo/redo crown this impressive font toolkit.andP;  Letraset USA has acquired the marketing rights for FRed, which will berenamed and released later this year.andP;  Contact Letraset, 40 Eisenhower Drive,Paramus, NJ 07653; (201) 845-6100.andO;</TEXT></DOC>